## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Approval not triggering on deal move | Approval check not integrated into stage change flow | Ensure control.checkApproval() is called BEFORE updateDealStage() |
| SLA cron not running | Vercel cron config missing | Add to vercel.json: crons array with /api/cron/sla-check |
| SLA timers showing wrong time | Timezone mismatch | Ensure deadline_at is stored in UTC, display converted to org timezone |
| Exception dialog not appearing | Control layer returning 'allowed' instead of 'blocked' | Check enforcement level — must be 'block', not 'warn' or 'log' |
| Handoff notes not blocking | Reassign button not checking control layer | Ensure control.validateHandoff() is called and returns complete=false |
| Campaign messages all identical | Marketing agent not receiving contact profiles | Verify crm_contact_profiles are computed before campaign planning |
| Profile computation slow | Too many contacts processed at once | Add batch processing with limit of 50 profiles per run |
| Workflow rollback creates duplicate | Version number not incrementing | Rollback creates a NEW version (max + 1), doesn't restore old number |
| Observability empty | Workflow log not capturing errors | Ensure try/catch in automation engine writes to workflow_log with error_category |
| Mobile showing wrong role view | Role not detected on app load | Check org_members query includes role field and is_active=true filter |

