## V4 Definition of Done

V4 is production-ready when:
- [ ] Control layer enforces all business rules (approvals, SLAs, exceptions)
- [ ] Pipeline is a true execution control system (stage gates, document requirements, inactivity enforcement)
- [ ] Workflow versioning supports safe iteration (draft → test → activate → rollback)
